  <span><%= image_tag("aws_logo.png", width: '55', height: '55', alt: 'S3 Login', class: "") %> Sign up for a free AWS account to generate Amazon S3 credentials. <a target="_blank" href="https://aws.amazon.com/free/">https://aws.amazon.com/free/</a></span>
</div>
