  <span><%= image_tag("ecs_logo.png", width: '55', height: '55', alt: 'S3 Login', class: "") %>Sign up for a free ECS Test Drive account to generate EMC S3 credentials. <a target="_blank" href="https://portal.ecstestdrive.com/">https://portal.ecstestdrive.com/</a></span>
</div>
